These are Puzzles for 3x6 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-3-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, tea, milk, coffee, water
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: parkour, climbing, baseball, surfing, soccer, handball
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: satire, thriller, western, spy, disaster, horror
 1. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is between the person watching spy movies and the person drinking mirinda##2
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
13. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
14. the person watching spy movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1
15. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |   5    |   6   |
| Beverage          | water | mirinda  | lemonade | tea      | coffee   | milk |
| Sport   | surfing  | parkour  | soccer    | climbing | handball | baseball |
| Movie-Genre     | thriller   | satire | horror     | spy      | western | disaster  |

