.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-3-2::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  accountant, musician, journalist, engineer, designer, electrician
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: rock, house, gospel, country, salsa, indie
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daffodil, tulip, bellflower, amaryllis, marigold, aconite
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
 2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 3. the musician is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is the fan of indie##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is the fan of rock##1
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the electrician##3
 7. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 8. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
 9. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who growstulip is on the right of the designer##1
11. the musician is on the right of the accountant##1
12. the fan of country is the musician##1
13. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of rock##1
14. the person who growsmarigold is the designer##1
15. the electrician is on the right of the journalist##1
16. the musician is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
17. the fan of house is on the left of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |     3      |    4     |      5      |     6      |
| Job    | journalist          | electrician  | accountant     | musician | designer | engineer       |
| Music-Genre   | indie | rock | house | country  | salsa  | gospel    |
| Flower   | daffodil      | aconite  | amaryllis | bellflower  | marigold      | tulip |

