.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-3-3::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: july, may, august, june, february, september
City: hannover, marseilles, new-york, liverpool, san-francisco, miami
The people have 6 different jobs:  designer, analyst, photographer, social-worker, entrepreneur, bartender
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the designer is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the bartender##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the analyst##1
 7. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the designer is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
10. the bartender is the person traveling to hannover##1
11. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's birthday is in august##1
12. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
13. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the social-worker##1
14. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
15. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6      |
| Birthday   | june        | february   | august     | july   | may           | september       |
| City   | marseilles | san-francisco | new-york | miami | liverpool     | hannover  |
| Job         | designer   | photographer  | social-worker   | analyst    | entrepreneur | bartender |

