.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: climbing, surfing, sailing, rugby, golf, biathlon
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: salsa, blues, trance, soul, d&b, techno
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, german, malaysian, japanese, mexican
 1. the fan of blues is the german##1
 2. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 3. the fan of salsa is on the left of the german##1
 4. the fan of trance is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the fan of soul is the malaysian##1
 7. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the argentine##1
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the chinese##3
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is the japanese##1
10. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the chinese##3
11. the chinese is on the left of the fan of blues##1
12. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the malaysian##1
13. the fan of soul is on the far left or far right##3
14. the japanese is on the right of the fan of blues##1
15. the mexican is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2      |   3    |    4     |     5     |    6    |
| Sport    | golf     | surfing | rugby | biathlon | sailing | climbing  |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | techno   | salsa  | blues  | trance   | d&b |
| Nationality     | malaysian | argentine         | chinese | german     | japanese     | mexican  |

