.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-3-5::.
6 different pets are kept: frog, chinchilla, pony, hamster, snake, ferret
The people have 6 different jobs:  firefighter, freelancer, engineer, librarian, teacher, writer
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: march, august, june, february, november, october
 1. the teacher is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is the owner of the hamster##1
 3. the owner of the pony is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the teacher is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
 6. the teacher is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in february##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the writer##3
 8. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the writer##3
 9. the firefighter is on the left or right of the teacher##3
10. the owner of the snake is the person who's birthday is in october##1
11. the librarian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
12. the engineer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
13. the person who's birthday is in october is the librarian##1
14. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
15. the owner of the frog is on the right of the firefighter##1
16. the teacher is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |   3   |     4      |    5     |     6      |
| Pet      | ferret      | pony | hamster | frog        | chinchilla   | snake     |
| Job   | freelancer | teacher         | firefighter   | writer       | engineer     | librarian     |
| Birthday         | february    | august       | june  | march | november | october |

