 1. the fan of country is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 4. the fan of punk is between the fan of country and the person traveling to rome##2
 5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 6. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
 7. the fan of country is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 8. the person who likes red is the fan of punk##1
 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
10. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
11. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
12. the fan of country is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
13. the fan of country is the person traveling to miami##1
14. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |      3      |    4    |       5        |      6       |
