 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
 5. the palace house is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 8. the person traveling to boston is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the craftsman house##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
11. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the craftsman house##1
12. the modern house is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
13. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
