 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person who likes soy-milkerman and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the person watching documentary movies is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
 7. the person who likes soy-milkerman is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 8. the person watching family movies is the person who likes azure##1
 9. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
10. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
11. the person who likes soy-milkerman is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
12. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who likes soy-milkerman##1
14. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
15. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who likes black##1

