The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: zombie, disaster, crime, sports, martial-arts, time-travel
 1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 3. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
 6. the person playing snooker is between the person driving the boat and the person playing poker##2
 7. the person watching zombie movies is the person playing canasta##1
 8. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
10. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
11. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is the person watching time-travel movies##1
13. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
14. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |     5     |      6      |
| Game   | monopoly      | backgammon       | mah-jongg       | canasta     | snooker    | poker |
| Transport       | motorbike | jet-ski      | quad-bike    | boat      | scooter | bike  |
| Movie-Genre      | time-travel  | martial-arts | disaster | zombie | crime   | sports     |

